          "continuity": "Ancient βλέπω 'I look, see'. Common throughout the Gospels ('βλέπε' — look!).",
          "forms": [ "βλέπω — I see", "βλέπεις — you see", "βλέπει — he/she/it sees" ],
          "phrases": [
