          "pos": "verb", "cat": "function", "rank": 30, "koine": "ἔρχομαι",
          "continuity": "Ancient ἔρχομαι 'I come, go' — a deponent (middle form, active sense), exactly as in Modern Greek.",
          "forms": [ "έρχομαι — I come", "έρχεσαι — you come", "έρχεται — he/she/it comes" ],
          "phrases": [
