          "continuity": "Ancient βιβλίον 'book, scroll' — the very word behind Bible and bibliography. The final -ν simply dropped in Modern Greek (βιβλίον → βιβλίο).",
          "forms": [ "το βιβλίο — the book", "ένα βιβλίο — a book" ],
          "phrases": [
            { "gr": "το βιβλίο", "en": "the book", "es": "el libro" },
